text: Wiwat Thaijaroen (Thai วิวัฒน์ ไทยเจริญ), is a Thai futsal Winger, and a member of Thailand national futsal team. AFC Futsal Championship: Thailand aim semi-finals He plays for Department of Highways Futsal Club in Futsal Thailand League. ==References== Wiwat Thaijaroen Category:1990 births Category:Living people Wiwat Thaijaroen Wiwat Thaijaroen Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in futsal Category:Competitors at the 2013 Southeast Asian Games
